WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Fish swimming together teaches us about addition and subtraction!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
When more fish join a group, we add them to our count.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
When some swim away to find food, we subtract from our total.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Ocean mathematics is everywhere we look!

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let's practice maths with our underwater friends!